    "created_at": "2016-11-10T18:05:48Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-11-10T18:05:48Z",
    "body": "If you can build the image you want to change the dock icon to as a `Buffer` or `data:` URL then you can create a `NativeImage` from it and set that as the icon using `app.dock.setIcon(icon)`.\n\nSo I'm not sure anything needs to be added to Electron to accomplish this as long as you can dynamically generate the image you want to set on the dock.\n\nYou can also use `app.dock.setBadge()` to apply simple text decoration.\n"
